<item>
            <title>[LU-3586] Kernel update [RHEL6.4 2.6.32-358.11.1]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3586</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RHEL6&apos;s kernel needs to be upgraded to the latest RHEL6.4 kernel since critical security vulnerability was reported.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/CVE-2013-2094&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/CVE-2013-2094&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, lustre-1.8 client needs to support RHEL6.4 kernel as well sooner.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
